replies.bodyText:
@jaikiran I know what you've outlined. However, the server provider factory overriding the rest client created one is not actually an issue as far as I've seen.
In such a situation, the providers rest client needs are registered by the server provider factory, and rest client works as expected.
The only problem situation is when rest client overrides the server provider factory, which this PR solves
